Package cz.cuni.mff.d3s.spl.interpretation

Individual interpretations of the SPL.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ComparisonResult
    Encapsulates result of a comparison of two data sources.
    Interpretation
    Encapsulates mathematical methods and approaches needed for evaluation of SPL formulas.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DistributionBasedComparisonResult
    Data set comparison result that uses probability distributions.
    DistributionLearningInterpretation
    SPL interpretation based on learning the distribution before deciding.
    DistributionLearningInterpretationParallel
    Parallel implementation of the DistributionLearningInterpretation.
    KindergartenInterpretation
    Primitive interpretation that merely compares arithmetic means.
    MannWhitneyInterpretation
    SPL interpretation based on Mann-Whitney test.
    WelchTestInterpretation
    SPL interpretation based on Welch's t-test.
    WelchTestWithEnlargedVariancesInterpretation
    SPL interpretation based on Welch's t-test with enlarged variances.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ComparisonResult.Relation
    Actual result of the comparison.
